WEBVTT

01:43.600 --> 01:44.680
A triple-flower mark?

01:53.840 --> 01:55.040
Li Jie's body

01:55.120 --> 01:57.040
was also transformed
from the six-eyed butterfly.

01:57.120 --> 01:59.440
Its strength reached
the triple-flower level long ago.

02:00.120 --> 02:02.160
But since he had
no sacred power of his own,

02:02.680 --> 02:04.360
the flower mark never appeared.

02:05.000 --> 02:07.240
Now that my soul

02:07.320 --> 02:09.320
has fused with his body,

02:09.400 --> 02:13.160
the triple-flower mark
naturally reveals itself.

02:14.200 --> 02:15.480
Well?

02:18.280 --> 02:20.400
Do you still think I'm insignificant now?

02:42.720 --> 02:43.680
Just as I thought.

02:44.920 --> 02:47.040
Looks like in all those rewinds,

02:47.120 --> 02:49.600
I never showed you the triple-flower mark.

02:50.280 --> 02:52.240
That's why you couldn't
withstand my strike.

02:52.800 --> 02:54.520
Well?

02:56.040 --> 02:58.640
Do you still think you're a deity now?

03:00.320 --> 03:01.800
What destroys a deity

03:02.400 --> 03:03.800
is not a devil,

03:04.920 --> 03:07.440
but the deity's own arrogance.

03:10.880 --> 03:12.800
Your body has reached its limit.

03:13.840 --> 03:15.640
This is the last rewind.

03:21.960 --> 03:23.800
I fought so hard to get here.

03:24.960 --> 03:27.160
I won't allow myself to lose to you.

03:59.760 --> 04:01.080
This time,

04:02.400 --> 04:04.120
I will succeed.

04:33.120 --> 04:34.080
See?

04:38.040 --> 04:39.400
I succeeded.

04:40.880 --> 04:42.920
Do you know why
I couldn't dodge your blade?

04:44.160 --> 04:46.520
Because I didn't want to.

04:49.040 --> 04:49.880
Break!

04:54.760 --> 05:00.760
Dragon hearts as one,
all to source return, all barriers break.

05:30.080 --> 05:31.240
It's raining!

05:39.280 --> 05:41.080
The drought is finally over.

05:41.160 --> 05:42.400
Luo'an is finally saved!

05:58.720 --> 05:59.840
I did it.

06:10.800 --> 06:11.720
Wu.

06:14.240 --> 06:15.720
Ji.

06:21.320 --> 06:22.800
I did it.

06:32.680 --> 06:33.640
Wu?

07:58.720 --> 07:59.560
This is for you.

08:06.960 --> 08:08.680
I'm sorry for staining

08:09.560 --> 08:10.560
your manuscript.

08:16.200 --> 08:18.000
Long, I…

08:19.120 --> 08:20.280
I promise I'll come back.

08:22.080 --> 08:23.040
Oh, right.

08:23.840 --> 08:26.240
I've asked my weasel brothers
to look after you.

08:27.200 --> 08:30.000
If anyone dares hurt you,
go ask them for help.

08:33.960 --> 08:36.000
I… I want to use this brush

08:36.080 --> 08:37.840
to write your story.

08:37.919 --> 08:40.960
When you come back next time,
I'll… I'll let you read it.

08:43.080 --> 08:44.360
Do you like it?

08:46.360 --> 08:50.160
You… You didn't make this
with your own fur, did you?

08:52.080 --> 08:53.120
Of course not.

09:24.240 --> 09:25.760
I was the one

09:25.840 --> 09:27.680
who forced the rain
to fall with demon magic.

09:28.720 --> 09:30.160
Why didn't I die?

09:33.840 --> 09:35.920
Some force even I do not know of

09:36.440 --> 09:37.560
was protecting you.

09:50.080 --> 09:51.280
But Ji Ling…

10:10.440 --> 10:12.240
People rarely get to have it both ways.

10:12.920 --> 10:14.520
He couldn't bear to let you die,

10:14.600 --> 10:16.640
but he also had to destroy Jiu Ying.

10:16.720 --> 10:19.640
Caught in that dilemma,
he suffered deeply.

10:20.400 --> 10:21.960
You destroyed the Dragon Deity's Power

10:22.520 --> 10:25.200
and ruined the mission
to which he'd devoted a century.

10:25.280 --> 10:28.160
And then he watched
your body and spirit vanish.

10:28.760 --> 10:30.040
That overwhelming despair and loneliness

10:30.120 --> 10:32.320
snuffed out the last bit of hope
in his heart.

10:33.640 --> 10:34.840
Thus,

10:35.640 --> 10:37.480
Lonescale consumed him.

10:38.800 --> 10:40.120
Lonescale lied to me.

10:41.240 --> 10:44.440
He said Ji Ling was a kind person.

10:44.520 --> 10:46.320
He said he chose to help me

10:46.400 --> 10:47.880
because he wanted to save Ji Ling too.

10:49.440 --> 10:51.240
I never thought it'd kill Ji Ling instead.

10:52.680 --> 10:55.000
You underestimated
how much you meant to him.

10:57.080 --> 10:59.720
You wanted him to live
and yourself to die.

10:59.800 --> 11:01.320
He wanted the opposite.

11:02.280 --> 11:05.920
Lonescale can rewind time
and peer into the past and future.

11:06.520 --> 11:08.280
How could he not have known
how it would end?

11:08.880 --> 11:10.760
He knew everything all along,

11:10.840 --> 11:12.280
and that was exactly why
he chose to help you.

11:13.240 --> 11:16.280
From beginning to end,
he had only one goal.

11:17.160 --> 11:19.480
To consume Ji Ling completely.

11:23.080 --> 11:25.320
I ruined your plan.

11:26.320 --> 11:28.200
You spent over 100 years
playing the Dragon Deity,

11:29.000 --> 11:31.720
alone and in pain,

11:33.640 --> 11:35.960
all just so you could reach
that very ending.

11:37.720 --> 11:39.520
But I couldn't stand by and watch you die.

11:40.840 --> 11:43.360
You shouldn't have existed in this world

11:43.440 --> 11:45.440
just to sacrifice yourself.

11:47.240 --> 11:48.680
That would've been too cruel to you.

11:52.560 --> 11:53.760
I never thought

11:56.960 --> 11:58.680
it would turn out like this.

12:07.760 --> 12:08.720
Ji Ling,

12:10.920 --> 12:12.760
can you hear me?

12:13.680 --> 12:15.320
Please wake up.

12:23.960 --> 12:25.440
Back then, I didn't understand

12:27.440 --> 12:29.080
why so many demons wanted

12:30.800 --> 12:31.880
to wear

12:32.880 --> 12:34.080
human skin

12:36.160 --> 12:37.480
and become human.

12:39.360 --> 12:42.600
A demon's tears are fake.

12:44.240 --> 12:47.440
They cry just to look more human.

12:48.760 --> 12:50.240
I don't understand

12:50.880 --> 12:52.080
why so many demons

12:52.760 --> 12:55.600
want to wear human skin

12:56.760 --> 12:58.040
and become human.

12:59.120 --> 13:00.640
But now I do.

13:11.880 --> 13:13.720
I want to be with you

13:16.000 --> 13:17.680
and live as the most ordinary of people,

13:19.600 --> 13:21.440
beginning work at sunrise

13:22.520 --> 13:24.040
and resting at sunset,

13:25.400 --> 13:26.680
walking hand in hand

13:27.760 --> 13:29.200
through the streets,

13:32.520 --> 13:33.840
and falling asleep

13:34.680 --> 13:36.040
in each other's arms at night.

13:54.400 --> 13:57.520
Ji Ling has been consumed by Lonescale
and remains unconscious.

13:58.040 --> 14:00.400
Bai Ze told us to go
to Chi Wen in the Dragon Abyss.

14:00.480 --> 14:02.640
He may have a way to save him.

14:04.200 --> 14:06.720
But without the last share
of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:06.800 --> 14:07.920
I can't become a dragon.

14:08.720 --> 14:10.160
When I get there,

14:10.680 --> 14:12.880
I don't know how I'll face my brother.

14:21.800 --> 14:22.880
Whether you become a dragon or not,

14:23.480 --> 14:24.600
you are still you,

14:26.600 --> 14:27.840
Wu Shiguang.

14:31.840 --> 14:34.400
You taught me in the Star Stone illusion

14:34.480 --> 14:36.160
that who we are

14:37.320 --> 14:39.920
has nothing to do
with background or bloodline.

14:40.440 --> 14:42.440
What matters more is whom we love

14:42.520 --> 14:44.200
and what we choose to protect.

14:46.240 --> 14:48.800
Besides, fortune and misfortune
go hand in hand.

14:49.400 --> 14:51.640
Without the last share
of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:51.720 --> 14:53.720
you will no longer
be able to kill Chi Wen,

14:53.800 --> 14:55.240
and Jiu Ying

14:55.880 --> 14:58.280
will stop trying to possess you.

15:00.160 --> 15:01.880
But if I can't become a dragon,

15:02.800 --> 15:04.320
I can't destroy the Oracle Stone.

15:05.200 --> 15:06.360
When the next full moon comes,

15:06.440 --> 15:08.280
you'll be forced back
to the Formless Moon.

15:08.360 --> 15:10.560
-I'm afraid…
-It's all right.

15:11.280 --> 15:12.320
There's still time.

15:14.920 --> 15:16.000
Besides,

15:17.560 --> 15:18.920
I can sever my tail.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.880
That's the worst possible choice.

15:25.960 --> 15:27.520
No, it isn't.

15:29.280 --> 15:31.320
I'm not like Xiaowei.

15:33.800 --> 15:35.480
I still have you.

15:48.280 --> 15:51.040
What do you think of this color?

15:57.800 --> 15:58.920
What do you think?

16:03.520 --> 16:05.440
Mortal couples bind
strands of their hair together.

16:06.840 --> 16:07.800
At first,

16:08.600 --> 16:10.320
I didn't understand what it meant.

16:11.120 --> 16:12.560
I only wanted a good omen.

16:14.000 --> 16:17.120
But when I braided
your hair together with mine,

16:17.840 --> 16:20.160
I realized that once
hair strands are entwined,

16:21.320 --> 16:22.400
unless they break,

16:23.040 --> 16:24.240
they are

16:25.680 --> 16:27.160
almost impossible to part.

16:28.040 --> 16:29.240
You and I are the same.

16:30.560 --> 16:32.400
We were fated to be entangled long ago.

16:34.240 --> 16:36.080
I will protect you no matter what

16:37.360 --> 16:39.160
and never fail this vow
sealed by our bound hair.

17:30.200 --> 17:31.280
You lied to me.

17:36.520 --> 17:37.760
I didn't.

17:38.720 --> 17:41.840
I truly hoped you'd be able to save him.

17:43.040 --> 17:45.440
What nurtured
that dragon scale into a demon

17:46.360 --> 17:48.440
was not only his loneliness

17:49.040 --> 17:50.840
but also his kindness.

17:51.520 --> 17:53.320
Then take me back again.

17:53.840 --> 17:55.360
I want to save him.

18:02.560 --> 18:03.600
It's useless.

18:05.160 --> 18:06.400
He remains unconscious

18:06.960 --> 18:08.720
because his consciousness

18:08.800 --> 18:10.560
has returned to the past.

18:11.880 --> 18:14.400
He's trapped in that part of his past
that came to haunt him.

18:17.720 --> 18:19.520
Haunt him?

18:20.720 --> 18:23.720
It's the old days before I was born.

18:35.640 --> 18:37.160
Then take me there.

18:38.280 --> 18:39.880
No matter how far back it is,

18:40.880 --> 18:42.200
I'm not afraid.

18:43.600 --> 18:44.920
I can take it.

18:48.960 --> 18:50.800
I know you can.

18:52.720 --> 18:54.400
And I can take you there

18:55.000 --> 18:58.880
so you can see why he became so lonely.

19:00.760 --> 19:01.880
But…

19:03.040 --> 19:04.120
But what?

19:06.040 --> 19:09.800
But that was more than 100 years ago.

19:10.760 --> 19:12.360
Far too long ago.

19:13.000 --> 19:15.600
No power can change it.

19:16.280 --> 19:18.800
So you won't be able to rewind time

19:19.360 --> 19:22.480
again and again like you did before
to alter the past.

19:23.720 --> 19:27.480
Besides, you did not

19:28.960 --> 19:30.320
exist there.

19:31.800 --> 19:36.000
Back then, there was no Lu Wuyi
by Ji Ling's side.

19:36.520 --> 19:39.360
You can only be a silent observer,

19:39.440 --> 19:41.880
unable to interfere in any way.

19:44.160 --> 19:45.560
Do you still want to go?

19:52.800 --> 19:54.040
This story

19:54.920 --> 19:56.040
is far too long.

19:57.040 --> 19:58.640
Even a day and a night wouldn't be enough.

19:59.320 --> 20:00.800
When we return from Luo'an,

20:01.400 --> 20:02.800
I'll tell it to you slowly.

20:14.440 --> 20:15.600
I do.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.440
I want to know

20:23.960 --> 20:25.320
his past.

21:00.440 --> 21:01.280
Yuan Xizai!

21:22.240 --> 21:25.040
A HUNDRED AND FIFTY YEARS AGO

22:07.560 --> 22:08.520
Xizai.

22:11.120 --> 22:13.560
Xizai? Xizai!

22:14.520 --> 22:17.320
Xizai. Xizai!

22:19.040 --> 22:20.000
Save him.

22:20.720 --> 22:21.680
Quick, save him!

22:23.280 --> 22:24.480
Save him!

22:26.800 --> 22:28.000
Where's your magic?

22:28.600 --> 22:29.880
Why don't you have any magic?

22:30.880 --> 22:32.200
Hurry up and heal him.

22:33.960 --> 22:36.840
Do it! Hurry! Save him!

22:37.800 --> 22:38.840
Save him!

22:40.960 --> 22:41.920
Wuhuo…

23:29.600 --> 23:32.600
Save my brother, and I'll let you go.

23:46.400 --> 23:47.720
It's almost New Year's Eve.

23:48.720 --> 23:50.440
Everyone, sort through
your things and throw out

23:50.520 --> 23:51.920
what you don't need.

23:52.000 --> 23:53.560
Sweep away the dust and grime,

23:53.640 --> 23:56.680
say goodbye to the old,
and welcome the new!

23:56.760 --> 23:59.880
I don't want to see you
live your whole life timid and weak,

23:59.960 --> 24:01.440
bullied by others.

24:01.520 --> 24:03.080
Take the Dragon Marrow

24:03.160 --> 24:04.640
and become

24:05.240 --> 24:06.680
a demon hunter like me.

24:07.360 --> 24:09.400
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

24:09.920 --> 24:12.080
I'm… I'm afraid of demons.

24:16.960 --> 24:17.880
Commander Yuan.

24:17.960 --> 24:20.000
YE DAOXUAN, ATTENDANT

24:20.080 --> 24:21.760
These were all Xizai's belongings.

24:22.840 --> 24:23.880
Throw them away.

24:25.560 --> 24:27.840
All right. That might be for the best.

24:58.120 --> 24:58.960
Master Daoxuan.

25:46.440 --> 25:49.640
The New Year's coming.
I've brought you something delicious.

25:50.880 --> 25:52.320
Maybe it'll help you

25:54.360 --> 25:56.000
recover your powers.

26:01.520 --> 26:03.040
Why do you have it?

26:04.400 --> 26:07.200
Let go. This isn't yours.

26:09.280 --> 26:10.680
It was all your fault.

26:13.200 --> 26:15.160
You wouldn't save my brother,

26:16.200 --> 26:18.200
so he died.

26:19.520 --> 26:20.840
Why?

26:20.920 --> 26:22.560
Why wouldn't you save him?

26:23.680 --> 26:25.400
Since you wouldn't save him,

26:27.520 --> 26:28.840
you can die too!

27:40.760 --> 27:41.960
Wuhuo,

27:42.640 --> 27:43.600
I'm afraid of demons.

27:51.360 --> 27:53.160
What… What kind of demon trick is this?

27:54.400 --> 27:55.440
I didn't do anything.

27:57.080 --> 27:58.920
I don't know any demon tricks.

28:03.080 --> 28:06.920
Did you think that if you took this form,
I wouldn't have the heart to kill you?

28:18.560 --> 28:20.640
-Wuhuo!
-Take it.

28:20.720 --> 28:22.000
-Swallow it!
-No!

28:22.080 --> 28:23.480
Swallow it!

28:47.880 --> 28:49.680
Give one to Xizai too. Here.

28:49.760 --> 28:52.320
-I've already eaten, Wuhuo.
-I don't care.

28:53.040 --> 28:54.360
Mother made them.

28:54.440 --> 28:55.480
Here. Eat one.

28:55.560 --> 28:56.760
I've eaten.

28:56.840 --> 28:58.360
Look how thin you are. Eat more.

28:58.440 --> 29:00.000
Go on. Eat.

29:00.080 --> 29:01.360
Eat more.

29:01.440 --> 29:03.560
Grow stronger, just like your brother.

29:05.000 --> 29:06.920
Wuhuo, you're amazing.

29:13.640 --> 29:15.760
Commander Yuan, I found it.

29:16.960 --> 29:19.800
It turns out the first skin a demon wears
to take human form

29:19.880 --> 29:21.680
uses blood as its medium.

29:24.600 --> 29:27.080
If its blood stains an object

29:27.160 --> 29:29.240
laden with intense emotion,

29:29.800 --> 29:32.600
the demon will naturally
take on the appearance

29:33.280 --> 29:34.560
of that object's owner.

29:43.800 --> 29:44.760
Commander Yuan,

29:45.960 --> 29:48.840
I thought you were looking up
remedies for the Wasting Sickness.

29:50.040 --> 29:51.480
Turns out it was this.

29:55.880 --> 29:58.640
How have you been feeling lately?

29:59.240 --> 30:02.480
Who would've thought the Meteor Blast
would cause the Wasting Sickness?

30:17.120 --> 30:20.000
I'm human now.
It's so inconvenient not having claws.

30:20.680 --> 30:22.280
I can't even leave marks.

30:47.680 --> 30:48.640
Thank you.

31:09.880 --> 31:13.280
Why do you sound like you're crying?

31:15.040 --> 31:18.840
Are… Are you sad?

31:21.000 --> 31:23.160
I don't know whether I'm sad

31:26.680 --> 31:28.200
or happy.

31:32.960 --> 31:35.000
I… I think I understand.

31:37.120 --> 31:40.440
Did I become someone

31:42.200 --> 31:43.360
you knew?

31:46.600 --> 31:47.640
Was that person

31:48.720 --> 31:50.400
very important to you?

31:54.240 --> 31:55.480
Father, Mother!

32:00.160 --> 32:02.360
Father! Father?

32:03.560 --> 32:05.040
-Mother…
-Wuhuo,

32:07.240 --> 32:08.240
it was the wolf demons.

32:09.440 --> 32:11.800
Take care of your little brother.

32:17.200 --> 32:18.240
And…

32:20.360 --> 32:22.400
don't tell him the truth.

32:22.480 --> 32:25.360
Xizai is timid.

32:31.640 --> 32:35.680
Wuhuo, why does it smell
so strongly of blood?

32:37.640 --> 32:39.640
It was rare for me to come home,

32:40.280 --> 32:42.240
so Father caught two wild chickens

32:42.800 --> 32:45.160
and stewed them for me.

32:45.920 --> 32:47.800
Father, Mother, and I talked it over.

32:49.600 --> 32:51.320
You should take the Dragon Marrow

32:52.360 --> 32:53.200
and become

32:54.200 --> 32:55.280
a demon hunter like me.

32:55.360 --> 32:56.320
No!

32:57.360 --> 32:59.320
Father and Mother would never agree to it!

32:59.840 --> 33:01.040
Even healthy, strong people

33:01.120 --> 33:03.600
often die after swallowing Dragon Marrow.

33:03.680 --> 33:04.800
Wuhuo,

33:05.880 --> 33:07.040
I'll die!

33:07.120 --> 33:08.920
Those were greedy fools

33:09.000 --> 33:11.240
who swallowed it recklessly
just to gain sacred power.

33:11.920 --> 33:13.880
The Shilin Sect tested my constitution.

33:14.480 --> 33:15.920
You're like me.

33:17.880 --> 33:18.880
You'll be fine.

33:18.960 --> 33:21.160
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

33:22.800 --> 33:24.040
I'm afraid of demons.

33:24.120 --> 33:25.120
If you're this cowardly,

33:25.720 --> 33:27.360
how will you survive
in this chaotic world?

33:29.800 --> 33:31.960
I never wanted to survive.

33:33.240 --> 33:35.720
I've already dragged our family down.

33:36.880 --> 33:37.840
Wuhuo,

33:41.080 --> 33:42.720
just let me die.

33:46.160 --> 33:47.120
All right?

34:09.639 --> 34:10.840
No need to be scared.

34:12.239 --> 34:15.560
They're firecrackers we set off
to celebrate New Year's Eve.

34:17.040 --> 34:19.800
What is New Year's Eve?

34:22.920 --> 34:23.960
New Year's Eve…

34:27.080 --> 34:28.679
Xizai, do you hear that?

34:28.760 --> 34:31.120
They're setting off firecrackers
and doing the dragon dance.

34:32.840 --> 34:34.000
I hear it.

34:39.080 --> 34:40.040
Look.

34:40.560 --> 34:41.920
How lively it is.

34:49.280 --> 34:51.080
Father, Mother!

34:51.159 --> 34:52.840
-Your brother is here.
-Wuhuo.

34:52.920 --> 34:54.280
-Father, Mother.
-You're here, Wuhuo.

34:54.360 --> 34:55.639
You've grown sturdier.

34:56.239 --> 34:58.520
-We missed you.
-I missed you too.

34:59.880 --> 35:02.000
Xizai, you've gotten so tall.

35:02.080 --> 35:03.480
Your mother made dumplings.

35:03.560 --> 35:05.400
-Mother made dumplings?
-Here.

35:05.480 --> 35:07.080
-Try it.
-Eat, Wuhuo.

35:07.160 --> 35:08.320
They're still hot.

35:10.840 --> 35:12.760
-Delicious.
-You like it?

35:12.840 --> 35:14.120
Give one to Xizai too.

35:14.200 --> 35:15.320
I've already eaten, Wuhuo.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.520
I don't care.

35:16.600 --> 35:17.560
-You're too thin.
-I've eaten.

35:17.640 --> 35:19.480
Here. Eat one.

35:19.560 --> 35:20.760
Go on. Eat.

35:27.560 --> 35:28.680
There's plenty more.

35:29.400 --> 35:30.880
New Year's Eve

35:31.720 --> 35:32.920
is the most beautiful

35:34.320 --> 35:36.240
and happiest day in the human world.

36:02.040 --> 36:03.120
Is this for me?

36:04.600 --> 36:05.560
It is.

36:06.360 --> 36:07.320
Eat.

36:08.680 --> 36:10.160
May you be free of misfortune

36:10.960 --> 36:12.160
in the coming year.

36:52.560 --> 36:54.360
Here. You eat some too.

36:57.640 --> 36:59.520
I've gotten grease all over your hands.

37:00.200 --> 37:02.520
It's all right. I'll wash them for you.

37:36.920 --> 37:39.240
You're a little fox.

37:39.920 --> 37:41.520
How can you not have fur?

37:43.160 --> 37:46.040
A bald fox will get laughed at.

37:46.840 --> 37:49.000
But my eyes can't see,

37:49.760 --> 37:53.120
so I don't know
if I've dressed you up nicely.

37:54.400 --> 37:55.920
As for your blade wound,

37:56.000 --> 37:58.520
I can't mend that yet.

37:59.680 --> 38:02.160
I am a nameless little fox.

38:02.760 --> 38:06.720
But my little fox can't go without a name.

38:07.600 --> 38:09.200
Foxes

38:09.720 --> 38:13.320
usually go "awoo, awoo."

38:14.080 --> 38:16.120
Why don't I call you

38:16.640 --> 38:17.480
Wu?

38:19.640 --> 38:20.600
Wu!

38:22.960 --> 38:23.920
Awoo!

38:38.440 --> 38:39.960
You don't have eyes either?

40:54.200 --> 40:55.400
What's wrong?

40:59.000 --> 41:00.160
What's going on?

41:02.520 --> 41:03.760
Hey, stop.

41:04.880 --> 41:06.560
It's all right.

41:14.640 --> 41:15.800
Here.

41:20.000 --> 41:22.200
Calm down. There, there.

41:23.560 --> 41:24.520
There, there.

41:26.240 --> 41:29.320
I'm in so much pain.

41:30.360 --> 41:32.040
It hurts so much.

41:34.240 --> 41:36.680
Father, Mother,

41:37.720 --> 41:40.320
take me with you.

41:40.400 --> 41:42.400
Take me with you.

41:42.960 --> 41:44.280
It's all right.

42:45.200 --> 42:47.640
You're awake. Are you all right now?

42:59.640 --> 43:00.720
What are you doing?

43:01.800 --> 43:03.080
Don't take it away!

43:04.240 --> 43:05.720
It's the only company I have!

43:05.800 --> 43:07.320
Can you give it back to me?

43:07.400 --> 43:09.160
Please give Wu back!

43:11.440 --> 43:12.480
Have you left?

43:46.080 --> 43:47.280
Eyes?

43:51.760 --> 43:55.320
You even stitched up the torn part.

44:22.920 --> 44:24.880
It's my return gift for last night.

44:27.520 --> 44:29.720
You know how to sew?

44:30.560 --> 44:31.960
My family was poor.

44:33.360 --> 44:34.960
My worn-out clothes would be passed down

44:35.480 --> 44:36.880
to my younger brother.

44:36.960 --> 44:38.520
The same piece of clothing

44:39.200 --> 44:40.840
would get patched over and over again.

44:41.680 --> 44:43.040
I did all the mending.

44:47.440 --> 44:48.400
Then why did you

44:48.960 --> 44:51.360
join the Shilin Sect?

44:52.280 --> 44:53.560
Who took care of your brother?

44:55.040 --> 44:56.560
My parents were poor,

44:57.920 --> 44:59.240
and I couldn't read either.

45:01.800 --> 45:02.920
My brother

45:04.520 --> 45:05.800
was sickly,

45:07.000 --> 45:08.720
and his treatment cost a lot of money.

45:09.880 --> 45:11.520
They said if a Shilin Sect hunter

45:11.600 --> 45:14.520
died fighting demons, the compensation

45:15.640 --> 45:17.800
would be enough to feed
a poor family for ten years.

45:19.040 --> 45:20.360
So I joined.

45:21.760 --> 45:23.040
What a pity.

45:26.040 --> 45:28.440
No amount of money means

45:31.320 --> 45:33.040
anything to me now.

45:34.240 --> 45:36.480
I don't have any family
left to care for now.

45:37.080 --> 45:38.040
I…

45:39.200 --> 45:41.480
I didn't mean to let your brother die.

45:42.440 --> 45:45.160
I was just an ordinary fox.

45:45.800 --> 45:47.360
I didn't know any magic at all.

45:48.520 --> 45:51.360
By the time I found you and your brother,

45:52.480 --> 45:55.840
the power Master Dragon Deity gave me
had already been used up.

45:58.120 --> 45:59.960
I don't have any family either,

46:02.200 --> 46:05.240
but I know losing family

46:06.000 --> 46:07.760
must hurt terribly.

46:11.760 --> 46:13.640
How could you not have any family?

46:15.120 --> 46:16.160
Aren't foxes

46:18.040 --> 46:19.720
born in litters?

46:27.840 --> 46:31.360
Maybe it was because I was born blind.

46:32.160 --> 46:36.040
My family abandoned me in a cave
and left me to fend for myself.

46:45.280 --> 46:47.320
I couldn't save your brother.

46:49.360 --> 46:51.160
How about I give you another brother?

46:55.880 --> 46:56.840
From now on,

46:58.440 --> 46:59.560
I'll be your younger brother.

47:51.960 --> 47:55.280
The war between humans and demons
is growing worse.

47:55.360 --> 47:56.880
All beings suffer.

47:57.480 --> 48:00.800
To end this war
and restore peace to the world,

48:00.880 --> 48:02.960
there is a mission
certain to end in death.

48:04.480 --> 48:05.960
Are you willing to do it?

48:10.880 --> 48:12.160
If you are,

48:13.400 --> 48:14.840
swallow this dragon scale.

48:34.560 --> 48:36.560
I'm already as good as dead.

48:39.400 --> 48:41.000
Of course I'm willing.

48:58.520 --> 48:59.760
What are you doing?

49:08.000 --> 49:09.520
I owe you a life.

49:11.200 --> 49:12.280
I'm paying it back.

49:32.800 --> 49:33.760
It hurts!
